<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Contract1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Contract,</orth> subst. 1) <emph>contráct,</emph> treaty, agreement: <cit><quote>c., succession . . . none,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.151" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 151</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>how joyful am I made by this c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.143" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 1, 143</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.156" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 156</bibl>. 2) <emph>contráct</emph> and <emph>cóntract,</emph> marriage-contract, espousals: <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.19" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 1.2.149" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 2, 149</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 3.1.223" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 223</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.209.223" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 209</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 2.3.185" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 3, 185</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.428" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 428</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.204" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 204</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.1.46" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 1, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.5.28" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.6" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 7, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.2.117" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 2, 117</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.3.120" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 3, 120</bibl>. <cit><quote>a c. of true love,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 84</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 84</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tn 5.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 159</bibl>. <cit><quote>the c. of her marriage,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.2.332" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 2, 332</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>his c. with Lady Lucy,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.5" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 7, 5</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.3.118" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. II, 3, 118</bibl>.
